text: Chang Chin-lan (; 1917–1975) was the first female judge in the Republic of China, as well as the first female justice on the Supreme Court of the Republic of China. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:1975 deaths Category:Chinese women judges Category:Taiwanese people from Shandong Category:Taiwanese women judges Category:Northwest University (China) alumni Category:Deaths from cancer in Taiwan
